OL,7,FPeers could be forced to resign if
OL,8,Fthey do not contribute enough to the
OL,9,FHouse of Lords, under reforms
OL,10,Fministers hope to make.
OL,12,FBaroness Smith of Basildon, the Leader
OL,13,Fof the House of Lords, also suggested
OL,14,Fthe Government is keen to press ahead
OL,15,Fwith plans to place a retirement age
OL,16,Fof 80 upon peers.
