OL,7,FThere are currently 86 hereditary
OL,8,Fpeers after the suspension of by-
OL,9,Felections pending the legislation, the
OL,10,Fmajority of whom ` 44 ` are
OL,11,FConservative.
OL,13,FThe Bill delivers on a promise in
OL,14,FLabour's election manifesto and has
OL,15,Fbeen promoted as the first step in a
OL,16,Fprocess of reform.
OL,18,FIn her Telegraph article, Lady Smith
OL,19,Fsaid the Government was now looking to
OL,20,Fprogress further changes to the upper
OL,21,Fchamber.
