OL,5,Cenough
OL,7,F"The introduction of a mandatory
OL,8,Fretirement age for peers and a
OL,9,Fparticipation requirement are both
OL,10,Fclear among our stage-two manifesto
OL,11,Fcommitments," she said.
OL,13,FThe Lords Leader said debates on the
OL,14,Fcurrent Bill have led her to believe
OL,15,Fthat there is room for a
OL,16,F"collaborative way forward".
OL,18,FA select committee of cross-party
OL,19,Fpeers will consider plans for a
OL,20,Fretirement age and a participation
OL,21,Frequirement, Lady Smith said.
